comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-14T18:51:32.468Z",lane-a-subagent-20260614,"Lane A src-coverage evidence update.\n\nWhat changed:\n- Extended `tests/unit/commands/register-commands.spec.ts` to cover additional register-operation and register-setup edge paths without adding new spec files:\n  - dependency-failed exit behavior when linked-test runs set `fail_on_skipped_triggered`\n  - extension/package lifecycle routing for adopt/adopt-all/activate/deactivate\n  - package install path normalization when no explicit target is provided\n  - doctor strict-exit behavior when summary status is `ok`\n- Extended `tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts` to cover malformed `inputSchema.required` fallback handling in `buildMcpToolContracts`.\n\nVerification run:\n1) `node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/register-commands.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts`\n   - PASS: 2 files, 69 tests.\n2) `CI=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage -- --coverage.thresholds.lines=0 --coverage.thresholds.branches=0 --coverage.thresholds.functions=0 --coverage.thresholds.statements=0`\n   - PASS: 158 files, 3388 tests.\n\nMeasured `src/**/*.ts` coverage delta (full-suite probe, thresholds disabled):\n- lines: 97.99% -> 98.00% (covered +4)\n- branches: 91.63% -> 91.64% (covered +1)\n- functions: 97.69% -> 97.78% (covered +4)\n- statements: 97.72% -> 97.74% (covered +4)\n\nTargeted file deltas:\n- `src/cli/register-setup.ts`: lines 92.17% -> 95.65%, functions 77.77% -> 88.88%\n- `src/mcp/tool-definitions.ts`: branches 66.66% -> 100%"
  "2026-06-14T21:06:44.629Z",lane-a-wave2-subagent-20260614,"Lane A wave2 strict all-source push (targeted hotspot branch lift).\n\nWhat changed:\n- Extended tests/unit/commands/register-commands.spec.ts with expanded option-path coverage for test/test-all/stats/health/validate/contracts, plus docs mutation and close fallback branches.\n- Extended tests/unit/schema-command.spec.ts with add-type/add-status human-format branch tests, case-insensitive alias show coverage, and wrapped non-Error parser/remover failure coverage.\n- Extended tests/unit/history-activity-command.spec.ts with history-redact type-path migration coverage (task -> custom type folder move).\n- Extended tests/unit/history-repair-command.spec.ts with unknown-author fallback/default-message coverage and rollback branch when history snapshot is unavailable.\n\nVerification:\n1) PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/register-commands.spec.ts tests/unit/schema-command.spec.ts tests/unit/history-activity-command.spec.ts tests/unit/history-repair-command.spec.ts\n   - PASS: 4 files, 146 tests.\n2) PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 pnpm exec vitest run tests/unit/commands/register-commands.spec.ts tests/unit/schema-command.spec.ts tests/unit/runtime-schema-command-flags.spec.ts tests/unit/history-activity-command.spec.ts tests/unit/history-repair-command.spec.ts tests/unit/history-rewrite.spec.ts --coverage.enabled true --coverage.include='src/cli/register-mutation.ts' --coverage.include='src/cli/register-operations.ts' --coverage.include='src/cli/commands/schema.ts' --coverage.include='src/cli/commands/history-redact.ts' --coverage.include='src/cli/commands/history-repair.ts' --coverage.reporter=text --coverage.reporter=json-summary --coverage.reportsDirectory=coverage/lane-a-wave2-after --coverage.thresholds.lines 0 --coverage.thresholds.branches 0 --coverage.thresholds.functions 0 --coverage.thresholds.statements 0\n   - PASS: 6 files, 172 tests.\n\nTargeted branch coverage deltas (before -> after):\n- src/cli/register-mutation.ts: 68.26% -> 70.98% (+2.72)\n- src/cli/register-operations.ts: 68.00% -> 80.00% (+12.00)\n- src/cli/commands/schema.ts: 71.50% -> 73.57% (+2.07)\n- src/cli/commands/history-redact.ts: 76.42% -> 77.14% (+0.72)\n- src/cli/commands/history-repair.ts: 79.41% -> 83.82% (+4.41)"
  "2026-06-15T03:26:12.331Z",claude-code-agent,"Lane A wave3 (opus orchestration, 2026-06-15): sub-agent lane-a-agent-20260614-opus ran ~40min (188 tool calls) before the account session-limit reset cut it off pre-documentation. Landed: new tests/unit/lane-a/pure-helpers-wave1.spec.ts + extended existing src specs (cli-main-errors, determinism, get-append-command, linked-test-parsers, migration-gates, mutation-projection, runtime-registrations, search-corpus, sentry-helpers, structure-exports, test-command). Behavior-preserving dead-branch eliminations (prove-dead over ignore, per ADR): append.ts/learnings.ts/notes.ts (resolveValue defined-when-flag-set casts), text-normalization.ts (jaccard union>=1 guaranteed), run-selectors.ts (match selector defined). Orchestrator verified the suite is green after fixing 2 cut-off-left broken specs."
